description:
Modded Minecraft. Welcome to a new season of modded Minecraft featuring the CrackPack!

This season we plan to engage is some friendly team rivalry by splitting the players into 2 main teams with everyone working together on each team to build up a base and fight the opposing team. Teams will be competing for player heads and a monument will be built in a neutral zone to show off the scores of each team.

Mod Pack: http://www.atlauncher.com/pack/TheCrackPack/
